author: Frank Torres
title: Olszewski announces District 1 fundraiser featuring local stars
text:
Olszewski announces District 1 fundraiser featuring local stars October 8, 2015 Pinterest 0 
Winter Garden Commissioner Robert “Bobby O” Olszewski has announced his next fundraiser for the Orange County Commission District 1 race, and this event features several local celebrities from the area. 
Boston Red Sox World Champion Johnny Damon , the first Orlando Magic Player ever drafted, Nick Anderson , as well as N’Sync superstar Joey Fatone are listed among others. 
Orange County Commission District 1 is district 1 is expected to be the most competitive county level race next year, with Olszewski facing project development manager Betsy VanderLey , whos also demonstrated strong support, including District 1 incumbent Commissioner Scott Boyd , who has reached term limits.
